Spray large skillet with cooking spray. Add chicken; cook and stir 5 min. on medium-high heat. Add green pepper and onion; cook 5 min. or until chicken is cooked through and vegetables are tender. Stir in tomatoes, water and Macaroni. Bring to boil. Reduce heat to low; cover. Simmer 10 min. or until macaroni is tender, stirring twice. Stir in Cheese Sauce until blended.